<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.6.8">
<l>uraikkiṉṟa mukkaṭpirāṉ yāṉē yeṉṉu muraikkiṉṟa ticaimukaṉ yāṉē yeṉṉu</l>
<l>muraikkiṉṟa vamararum yāṉē yeṉṉu muraikkiṉṟa vamarar kōṉ yāṉē yeṉṉu</l>
<l>muraikkiṉṟa muṉivarum yāṉē yeṉṉu muraikkiṉṟa mukilvaṇṇa ṉēṟak kolō</l>
<l>vuraikkiṉṟa vulakat tīrkkeṉ collukē ṉuraikkiṉṟa veṉkō maḷavoṇ koṭikkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“I [am] the three-eyed lord that is talked of”, she says,</l>
	<l>“I [am] the one with a face in [each] direction that is talked of”, she says,</l>
<l>“I [am] all the immortals that are talked of”, she says,</l>
	<l>“I [am] the king of the immortals that are talked of”, she says,</l>
<l>“I [am] all the sages that are talked of”, she says,</l>
	<l>while the one with cloud colour who is talked of settles in [her]?</l>
<l>What will I say to you of the world that is talked of,</l>
	<l>about my tender bright creeper that is talked of?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
